    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight Dirty! is an online arena shooter inspired by Liero, Broforce and Rounds for up to 6 players.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realtime online multiplayer with a server list and online chat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully destructible terrain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable character selection</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 levels (of customizable sizes) to terraform</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 different weapons to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 upgrades to choose from</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Full Version Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levelling and Ranked modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More customization options for your characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited custom levels with workshop support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements, stats and leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ upgrades</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775020/extras/36aa44c54fb3465e42037e39e8080da0.gif?t=1747318117\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775020/extras/36aa44c54fb3465e42037e39e8080da0.poster.avif?t=1747318117\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p>",
